item.description:
“Planting the seeds to grow your future… It might be time to finally take those goals off the shelf!” This interactive collaborative roundtable discussion will inspire and motivate you!

Our membership includes a wealth of experience, information and wisdom. From business coaches, to women who have been in your shoes there is someone to help you achieve the next level in your business.

Come with a clearly defined goal to grow your business.

Our host Lisa Lelas will contribute her considerable facilitation skills to be sure the meeting runs smoothly.
item.name: Our annual Interactive Brainstorming Meeting
